list.name: Default
list.comment:
Added constructor to abstractRobot. Added hitPoints field to abstract robot. Added class testRobot to create a robot for testing.
Implemented move method in abstractRobot, robots can now be moved across the board. Implemented temporary draw method in abstractRobot, robots are now represented by a blue square and a string showing the direction. Implemented a moveForwardOne method in testRobot to move the robot one tile in the direction it is facing.

task.summary: Started working on some basic stuff for the board, frame and IO. To make the project move towards it's first milestone. Had to do some thinking about how to structure the tiles for the board. Still not sure I've chosen the right one. Also in the board maybe a generic method that goes through the tiles and can be used to do different things would reduce code repetition.

New Game class to start, stop, pause the game and to contain gamestuff like score...
Problem, accidentally ran startGame in both constructor and then in the mainloop but removed it from the gameloop so now it's just one window.
